body: Can we switch Avery from Monday to Wednesday this week?
Yes. I moved it to Wednesday at 5 PM and updated the tutor.
Blake has a school event Thursday. Any open Sunday slots?
We can do Sunday at 2 PM. I reserved it for now.
Casey is behind on fractions. Can we focus next session there?
Absolutely. I added fractions as the top priority for this week.
Can Emerson do virtual today instead of in person?
Yes. I sent the video link and notes to the tutor.
Gray will be 10 minutes late. Should we still come?
Yes, please come. We will shorten warm up and keep core practice.
Jules finished the homework packet early.
Great progress. We will move to multi step word problems next.
Can Kai get two sessions next week before the quiz?
Yes. I added Tuesday and Thursday at 6 PM.
Logan is anxious about chemistry labs.
Understood. Tutor will run a lab write up walkthrough first.
Can we pause Oakley for one week due to travel?
Yes, I marked next week as skipped and no hours will be used.
Quinn is unassigned right now. Any tutor openings this Sunday?
Yes, I can place Quinn Sunday at 3 PM pending confirmation.
Skyler asked for more algebra and less test drills.
Noted. I updated the lesson plan to shift toward algebra practice.
General question: do you have any spots for a sibling intake?
Yes, please submit a new intake and I can review it this week.
